abstract: >-
  A statistical tool for detecting AI-generated writing patterns in prose.
  Uses log-odds ratio analysis to identify words, phrases, and structural
  patterns that are overrepresented in LLM output compared to human writing.
  Provides scoring, detailed findings, and interactive fixing capabilities.
